/**
 * Authoritative hitbox geometry in texture-local space (Java `game.config.HitboxValues`).
 * Regenerated by desktop HitboxEditor — do not invent polygons.
 *
 * Roles: COLLISION / PLAYER / ENEMY_* — solids / world.
 * *_HIT / offensive strips — deal damage. *_HURT / PLAYER_HURT — receive damage.
 * Pickups: pickup() = collection (Hit), pickupPhysics() = tile collision.
 */

